        <hr noshade size="1">
        
        <font color="white" face="Verdana, Arial, Helvetica" size="2">Ok.</P><P>First things first:</P><P>Mobs will summon you if you are on their agro list, and they are damaged.</P><P>PoGs have an agro range of the entire zone.</P><P>Therefore, if you zone in, another guild got killed by them, and they are down HP, you will get summoned if they can sense you.</P><P>Want to mess up a raid?  Hit a pog with Touch of night, and feign, the other raid there will get summoned to their deaths :)</P><P>As for them disappearing?  Thats probably a bug...</P><P></P><P>Zrazzt the Warduck<a href="#top"><img src="icon_go_up.gif" height=15 width=15 border="0" align="right" alt="Go to Top of Page"></a></font></td>
